254
28:42.420 --> 28:49.740
Just a few quick remarks
about teleportation before moving on to the
second example of the lesson, which is superdense coding.

255
28:49.740 --> 28:57.900
First, I think it's important to clarify that teleportation is not an application of quantum information, it's a protocol

