28:57.900 --> 29:03.510
and specifically it's a
protocol for performing quantum communication.

257
29:03.510 --> 29:12.660
In order for teleportation
as I've described it to be useful, there has to be some reason for performing quantum communication.

258
29:12.660 --> 29:19.170
Second, it's reasonable to speculate that teleportation could, one
day, become a standard way

259
29:19.170 --> 29:26.730
